  "title": "Intel's Itanium: Ready and Desirable for Mainframe-Class Workloads",
  "description": "Aberdeen Group white paper examining whether Intel Itanium processors are ready to handle mainframe-class workloads. Based on interviews with migration users and a survey of 98 mainframe users, the study finds that Itanium platforms match or exceed mainframes in performance, scalability, and cost-effectiveness while being equally robust.",
